title: Couple With Heart Man Man Light Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone
description: Illustrates a romantic bond between two men with different skin tones, one light and one dark, celebrating love and diversity in relationships.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's rendering of this couple emoji, featuring two men with light and dark skin tones, portrays them standing close together, enveloped by a prominent, vibrant red heart. The design on Apple devices emphasizes smooth, rounded forms and realistic lighting, giving the figures a warm and affectionate appearance. This emoji beautifully symbolizes love, partnership, and romantic relationships between two men, celebrating diversity and inclusion.
